  "legal_bases": [
    {
      "type": "act",
      "identifier": "Instrument of first designation - Charter of the United Nations Act 1945 Listing 2011 (No 1) [F2021L00641, Gazette No. S 178, 16 November 2011]. The Minister for Foreign Affairs listed this individual on 16 November 2011 under subsection 15(1) of the Charter of the United Nations Act 1945 (CotUNA), pursuant to Australia's obligations under UNSC resolution 1373 (2001).  The Minister declared on 16 November 2014 and subsequently on 26 October 2017 and 12 October 2020 pursuant to subsection 15A(2) of CotUNA, that this listing would continue to have effect. The Minister listed this individual afresh on 11 October 2023.",
      "title": "Instrument of first designation - Charter of the United Nations Act 1945 Listing 2011 (No 1) [F2021L00641, Gazette No. S 178, 16 November 2011]. The Minister for Foreign Affairs listed this individual on 16 November 2011 under subsection 15(1) of the Charter of the United Nations Act 1945 (CotUNA), pursuant to Australia's obligations under UNSC resolution 1373 (2001).  The Minister declared on 16 November 2014 and subsequently on 26 October 2017 and 12 October 2020 pursuant to subsection 15A(2) of CotUNA, that this listing would continue to have effect. The Minister listed this individual afresh on 11 October 2023."
